DESCRIPTION:<span><span><span> </span></span></span><span><br><span><b><i
 ><span>Aprilmeeting changed to Zoom meeting April 8\, 7pm.</span></i></b><
 span><br>Email <a href="mailto:greenteam@fccmtc.com" target="_blank"><span
 >greenteam@fccmtc.com</span></a> for Zoom link.</span></span></span><br><s
 pan><span><span> </span></span></span><br><span><span><span>Green Team/Cr
 eation Justice Ministry monthly meetings: 2nd Sunday of the month\, after 
 worship\, in the FCC library. </span> <span><span><span>Our congregation 
 is committed to the idea that creation care is central to each aspect of 
