UID:10138271-1775998800-1776007800@montclairlocal.news
SUMMARY:Rug Tufting Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Learn how to make your own custom rug! This rug tufting class will guide you through creating your own custom rug using a tufting gun. You’ll learn essential techniques for handling the tufting gun safely and effectively\, focusing entirely on mastering the craft since your design and yarn colors will already be prepared on the tufting frame. Once tufting is complete\, you’ll discover how to apply glue and backing to secure and protect your rug. The class finishes with the exciting step of trimming excess yarn\, revealing the final texture and look of your handmade rug. This hands-on experience combines creativity with practical skills to help you craft a unique\, personalized piece. \nUpon booking you will receive a link to choose your rug design for the class. \nThis is a great opportunity to make a fun gift\, to keep or to give. Invite your partner\, friends\, family\, or coworkers for a fun and creative day out. \nBring a mask if you are sensitive to yarn particles and chemical smells from glue. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/rug-tufting-workshop/
LOCATION:The Eclectic Chic Boutique\, 547 Bloomfield Avenue\, Montclair\, NJ\, 07042\, United States
