CREATED:20260325T160505Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260325T160505Z
UID:10139417-1776016800-1776025800@montclairlocal.news
SUMMARY:Learn How to Get Published with the Book Doctors
DESCRIPTION:As part of its ongoing writers’ workshop series\, Watchung Booksellers hosts authors Arielle Eckstut and David Henry Sterry\, aka The Book Doctors\, to share insights on how to get published. The workshop will be held on Sunday\, April 12 from 6-8:30 p.m. \nThis workshop will take you through the four primary paths to publication\, choosing the right idea\, crafting an attention-getting pitch and query\, and finding the right agent/publisher. You’ll be armed with knowledge before pitching your idea at Pitch-a-palooza during the Montclair Lit Fest! \nDavid Henry Sterry & Arielle Eckstut are co-founders of the Book Doctors. They are co-authors of The Essential Guide to Getting Your Book Published: How To Write It\, Sell It\, and Market It… Successfully. Tickets are $80 for the class and can be purchased at watchungbooksellers.com/events/writers-workshops \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/learn-how-to-get-published-with-the-book-doctors/
CATEGORIES:Art & Culture,Community,Literature
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/aprilwkshop.png
END:VEVENT
