DESCRIPTION:This workshop helps students navigate the unspoken rules of co
 rporate culture while building confidence in professional settings. Atten
 dees will learn how to present themselves effectively\, communicate with 
 intention\, and make strong first impressions\, along with practical stra
 tegies for asking for mentors\, securing internships\, and approaching op
 portunities through cold emailing and cold calling.\n\nHosted by: Associa
 tion of Latino Professionals For America\n\nAdditional Information can be
