LAST-MODIFIED:20260326T181715Z
UID:10139437-1776193200-1776200400@montclairlocal.news
SUMMARY:She Leads with Purpose: A Women’s Leadership Workshop with Nicole & Lauren
DESCRIPTION:Great leadership today requires more than performance. It requires clarity\, authenticity\, and the courage to lead in alignment with who you truly are. \nThis Women’s History Month\, join a dynamic community of corporate leaders\, founders\, entrepreneurs\, and women in management roles who are committed to leading with purpose. \nWe’ll begin with a quick well-being check-in to measure where you are showing up at your strongest and where greater alignment may unlock more energy\, impact\, and fulfillment in your leadership. \nFrom there\, we’ll explore how women can lead more powerfully by leveraging their unique strengths\, values\, and voice and by defining success on their own terms. \nThis workshop brings together accomplished women who are committed to leading with intention\, expanding their influence\, and supporting one another’s growth. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/she-leads-with-purpose-a-womens-leadership-workshop-with-nicole-lauren/
CATEGORIES:General Events
