SUMMARY:Graphic Novel Book Club (18 )
DESCRIPTION:Do you like AFRO-FUTURISM or want to learn more about 
 it??\n\nIF YES\, THEN THIS MONTH IS FOR YOU!\n\nWe will be discussing BTTM 
 FDRS an afro-futuristic horror-comedy about gentrification\, hip-hop\, and 
 cultural appropriation.\n\n\n \n\nBTTM FDRS: By Ezra Claytan 
 Daniels\n\nCopies of the book will be available to pick up at the BAB 
 Library. Check Hoopla and Libby for digital copies!\n\nRegistration is 
 required.
