CREATED:20260115T194355Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260115T194355Z
UID:10136548-1776238200-1776288600@montclairlocal.news
SUMMARY:The Elementary Spacetime Show
DESCRIPTION:A highly inventive new musical by César Alvarez and Emily Orling\, The Elementary Spacetime Show tells the story of Alameda: a young girl who enters a liminal void somewhere in between life and death. Alameda must pass through the eight existential trials of a cosmic Vaudevillian game show to discover the possibility that her darkness is a gift. Her journey is set to a kaleidoscopic contemporary score that bravely handles the subject of teenage suicide with both sensitivity and vibrant showmanship\, blending sly humor with emotional nuance. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/the-elementary-spacetime-show/2026-04-15/
LOCATION:Alexander Kasser Theater\, Montclair State University\, Montclair\, NJ\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art & Culture,Beauty,Live Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/elementary_spacetime_show_800x800.png
GEO:40.8615199;-74.1985521
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Alexander Kasser Theater Montclair State University Montclair NJ 07042 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=Montclair State University:geo:-74.1985521,40.8615199
END:VEVENT
