SUMMARY:Jewish Mysticism: Tracing the History of Kabbalah
DESCRIPTION:  \nThis online adult education class is offered through The Melton School and is taught by Rabbi Marc Katz on Wednesday mornings at 11:00am. Registration is required. For more information on the course offering\, email Rhonda Lilienthal at rlilianthal@jccmetrowest.org or call 973-530-3519. To register\, email Rachel Davis at rdavis1@jccmetrowest.org or call 973-530-3989. A Zoom link for class will be distributed to all registered students as we approach the first class.
