SUMMARY:Beginners in The Work of Byron Katie: Newcomers Welcome
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\nA free Zoom meditation session designed wi
 th newcomers in mind. Sessions will include at least one hour of facilitat
 ion (meditation) and there is room for questions and answers throughout. I
 f you're curious about The Work\, you're invited to join!\n\nSee you there
 !\n\nPlease be aware that sessions will close if no members have joined af
 ter 10 minutes.\n\n**To book a free introductory private session with Emry
 s\, [click here](https://calendly.com/mindfulnesswithemrys/onehoursession)
 [.](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)**\n\nEmrys also organises
  a free Work of Byron Katie Meetup group. Visit: [https://www.meetup.com/t
 hework-runsfree](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/)\n\n*Find out mo
 re about Emrys [here](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)[.](http
 ://linktr.ee/theworkrunsfree)*\n\nTo best prepare for each session\, compl
 ete a *Judge Your Neighbour* worksheet free at [https://thework.com/part-t
 hree/](https://thework.com/part-three/) or visit [http://www.thework.com](
 http://www.thework.com)
