SUMMARY:AAPI NJ Presents Comedy Night
DESCRIPTION:AAPI New Jersey Presents: Comedy Night! \n\nCome out\, unwind\, and share some laughs with your community! We’ve put together a fantastic night of stand-up comedy featuring some seriously talented folks:\n\nAlyce Chan — creator of the beloved Mom Com NYC\nCraig Baldo\n\nSandeep Sen\n\n\nJuno Men\n\n\nWhether you’re a comedy regular or just looking for a fun night out with good people — this one’s for you. Come as you are\, bring a friend\, and let’s make some memories together. \n\n—\nHosted by the warm and wonderful Cindy\, Mona & Neha\, who promise a night full of good energy\, great laughs\, and even better company. \n\nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
