SUMMARY:Beginner Mah Jongg - Fri. Midday - Main
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nLooking for more fun in your life? Need an excuse to see your 
 friends without eating? Worried about dementia? Learn how to play the 
 ancient Chinese game of Mah Jongg! This game is not hard to play but 
 complex to learn. My method of teaching is guaranteed to have you playing 
 with strategy by the end of the session. Please bring $15 to the first 
 lesson to purchase a Mah Jongg card.\n\n \n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Conference Room\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Games
