SUMMARY:Botanical Drawing Workshop
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nWelcome spring by immersing yourself in the captivating world 
 of botanical artistry. This all-day workshop welcomes participants of all 
 skill levels and takes place in a supportive\, encouraging environment 
 where creativity can truly flourish.\n\nExplore a new way to hone your 
 observational skills as you discover the magic of translating nature’s 
 beauty onto paper using regular and watercolor colored 
 pencils.\n\nDemonstrations will guide how to capture details ranging from 
 the delicate curves of petals to instruction on how to achieve color 
 accuracy. Constructive guidance to help you refine your technique towards 
 developing your individual artistic style will also be given.\n\nNote: Art 
 supplies are not included and must be purchased in advance of this 
 workshop. Materials should cost approximately $80. Visit the link below to 
 view the list of materials needed for this workshop. 
 \nhttps://www.heidisandecki.com/art-supplies-botanical-drawing-workshop
LOCATION:Montclair - Cornerstone Montclair\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Arts & Crafts
