 tive and creative activities. Participants can join a live NBA‑themed Kah
 oot trivia game 🏀 featuring questions about teams\, players\, mascots\, 
 and league history\, encouraging friendly competition and community build
 ing. At the same time\, a coloring station 🎨 will offer NBA‑inspired des
 igns and art materials\, providing a relaxing\, low‑pressure outlet for c
 reativity and stress relief. Together\, these elements celebrate the star
 t of the NBA season.\nEnjoy Great Food\, Giveaways\, Prizes & NBA Games! 
 \nLocation: Franklin Hall - Second Floor Theater - Room 214 (Bloomfield C
 ampus)\n\nHosted by: Bloomfield's Office of Residence Life\n\nAdditional 
 Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/even
 t/12408197
