 register.\n\nPractical French 2 is a continuation of French 1. Master 
 additional grammar\, more advanced verbs and vocabulary. Conversation is an 
 essential component for those who wish to focus on more speaking and proper 
 pronunciation. Students who are considered advanced beginners are welcome 
 to join the class.
