DESCRIPTION:\n\nA mind-body conditioning technique that focuses on trunk s
 tability and coordinated breathing through a series of exercises.  Pilate
 s develops a longer\, leaner\, stronger\, and more graceful body by impro
 ving muscular symmetry\, alignment\, posture\, core strength\, and flexib
 ility. All levels are welcome.\n\n\nHow do I Sign-up?\n\nRegistration is 
 not required.\nFREE for students with a valid Montclair State ID\n\nWhere
  and When?\n\nEvery Tuesday\, Jan 20 - April 24\n10:15 - 11 a.m.\nStudent
  Recreation Center - Multipurpose Room 1\n\n\n\n\n\nInstructor - Bridget\
 n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Information can be found at
 : https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12065321
