SUMMARY:Read to KoKo the Therapy Dog
DESCRIPTION:Come read aloud to KoKo the therapy dog\, a dear friend of the 
 library! \n\nWould you like to practice reading aloud with expression and 
 fluency? Or would you like to spend time with a furry friend to bring a 
 smile to your face? Well\, you can do both by reading aloud to KoKo the 
 Therapy Dog. Please sign up for a 10 minute slot to get cozy with KoKo and 
 share a good book. We will provide a variety of books to choose.\n\nSIGN UP 
 HERE for your slot!\n\nThis is not a drop-in event. Registration is 
 required. (You may ONLY sign up on the above Sign-Up Genius link. Please 
 sign up only once a month so that other children can have a turn.)\n\n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Storytime Room\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Library":MAILTO:events@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Children's Programs, Health & Wellness, Storytime
