DESCRIPTION:Join us for Chessnuts\, hosted by Montclair High's Chess Club! 
 They'll teach you everything you need to know and help you hone your skills 
 as a player.\nRegistration required.\n\nMeet your instructors:\nFrankie 
 McGrath is a HS sophomore\, avid chess player\, and top member of the 
 Montclair High School Chess Team. Frankie has been playing chess since he 
 was 5 years old and is excited to share his love of chess with the 
 community.\n\nSign up for the Monthly Teen Newsletter\n
