DESCRIPTION:Join the CAs for the Hawk Crossings Closing Building Meeting!\
 nDuring these meetings\, the CAs will provide information about the guide
 lines and expectations with moving out\, living on campus\, and informati
 on to Hawk Crossings specifically. You only need to attend one meeting as
  the information will be the same at every meeting. Attendance will be ta
