DESCRIPTION:Testimony Night is a powerful and intentional gathering where 
 individuals come together to share real stories of how God has moved in t
 heir lives. This is a space for honesty\, healing\, and encouragement—whe
 re people can be open about their journeys\, struggles\, growth\, and vic
 tories through Christ.\nThis event is open to all—men and women\, no matt
 er where you are in your faith. Whether you’re strong in your walk\, stil
 l growing\, or just curious\, you are welcome here.\nThere is power in te
 stimony. Hearing how God has worked in someone else’s life can inspire ho
 pe\, strengthen your faith\, and remind you that you’re not alone in what
  you’re going through.\nCome with an open heart\, ready to listen\, conne
 ct\, and experience a night of real stories\, real people\, and a real Go
 d.\n\nHosted by: I lift Jesus\, MSU Pensa\n\nAdditional Information can b
 e found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12408221
