 \, and see the democratic process in action. You’ll tour the NJ State Cap
 itol\, connect with legislators\, and advocate for your community. The be
 st part? It’s all FREE (transportation + lunch included)!\nNetwork with l
 ike-minded professionals\, engage in politics\, and develop a new perspec
 tive on the legislative process.\nDon’t just learn about change… be part 
 of it.\n📍 Transportation will be provided from the Red Hawk Deck on Coll
 ege Ave\, Montclair\, NJ\, 07043 and from Bloomfield Campus\n\nHosted by:
  Government Relations and Community Affairs \n\nAdditional Information ca
 n be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12371075
