DESCRIPTION:Black Girl Recess is a welcoming and affirming space designed 
 to encourage rest\, reflection\, and connection for women on campus. Whil
 e the event centers the experiences of Black women\, any young woman on c
 ampus who feels this space would be meaningful to her is encouraged to at
 tend.\nThis event provides an opportunity for participants to step away f
 rom daily responsibilities and engage in open conversation around self-ca
 re\, balance\, and personal well-being. Attendees will reflect on the man
 y roles they navigate in their academic and personal lives and explore he
 althy ways to manage stress\, prioritize themselves\, and support one ano
 ther.\n \nThe event will include interactive stations\, open conversation
 \, and opportunities for reflection in a relaxed and affirming environmen
 t. Black Girl Recess promotes self-care\, balance\, and empowerment while
  fostering meaningful connection and support among participants.\n\nHoste
 d by: Bloomfield Swing Phi Swing Social Fellowship\, Inc.\n\nAdditional I
 nformation can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event
 /12139475
DTEND:20260423T003000Z
