DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special storytime just for our tiniest patrons! 
 We'll sing songs\, nursery rhymes\, and read a few board books geared 
 towards those from ages birth-23 months in our Kid’s Place. If weather 
 permits\, storytime will take place outside\, please bring a blanket to sit 
