SUMMARY:The Corner Book Club Meeting
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a lively\, librarian-led discussion of bestselling 
 author Robert Harris's thrilling novel\, Munich.  This is a work of 
 historical fiction set in the 1930s when British Prime Minister Chamberlain 
 and Hitler were scheduled to have a last-ditch meeting to stave off armed 
 conflict.  Registration is recommended.
