DESCRIPTION:World’s Fair Day is an annual campus-wide event that celebrate
 s the richness of Montclair State University. Organizations\, Offices and
  Departments take part in the event by tabling\, sharing information\, de
 licious foods\, and through performances. This day will be filled with fo
 od tastings\, performances\, giveaways and so much more! Come check out d
 ifferent clubs and organizations and see what fun they bring to the table
  to teach you about different cultures! Mark your calendars\, you won't w
 ant to miss this!\n \nAll are invited!\n\nHosted by: Athletics\, Advocacy
