SUMMARY:Making Words (Grades 1-3)
DESCRIPTION:Try out this FUN hands-on activity to practice word patterns\, 
 taking apart sounds\, phonemic awareness and spelling.\n\nChildren will 
 participate in an activity using letter tiles to practice phonics\, 
 phonemic awareness\, word patterns and spelling. This fast-paced hands-on 
 practice is great for mastering letter and sound relationships for stronger 
 decoding skills. Let's see if we can figure out the mystery word at the 
 end! If time allows\, children will also have time to play word games or 
 make a craft.\n\nSign-up required.
