SUMMARY:[MILL Senior Friday] Chair Yoga for Everyone with Pammi
DESCRIPTION:Join us on Fridays for a day full of events for Seniors with 
 the MILL @ MPL! All events are free and open to the public. Registration is 
 recommended unless otherwise noted.\n\n\nWith this class there is a focus 
 on basic yoga postures\, breathing techniques\, meditation and supported 
 standing poses for balance\, range of motion and flexibility. Most of the 
 class is done in a chair or the chair can also be used to support 
 balance.\n\nABOUT THE INSTRUCTOR\nPAMMI ANANDANI is a certified yoga 
 instructor specializing in teaching a chair yoga style called Yoga for 
 Everyone. She has taught yoga to seniors at Riverdale Y\, Lennox Hill 
 Neighborhood House and Cedar Grove Seniors among others.\n\nHOW TO 
 REGISTER\nThis class is run by the MILL. Please register for classes 
 directly through their website here.\n\nFor questions about MILL classes 
 please call 973-744-3278.\n\nMILL @ MPL is made possible through a 
 partnership between the MILL\, Montclair Public Library and Partners for 
 Health.
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Auditorium
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Library":MAILTO:events@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult Services, Fitness, Health & Wellness
UID:LibCal-10306-16669738
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/16669738
END:VEVENT
