SUMMARY:Beginning Ukulele
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nAloha!  In this beginner’s ukulele class you will learn 
 basic chords and strums and some fun\, easy songs.  No music background or 
 experience necessary.  We will also listen to some ukulele luminaries from 
 the past and present: Ukulele Ike\, Roy Smeck\, Tiny Tim and Jake 
 Shimobukuro.  \n\nStudents should bring their own ukuleles to class.
