 at the Student Recreation Center Pool. You and your family will have FREE
  use of our pool and locker rooms (no membership to the facility is requi
 red). Flotation devices are allowed as long as they are USCG approved. We
  have life jackets available - just ask the lifeguard.\n \nPlease note th
 e following:\n\nBring your Montclair ID in order to check-in.\nNo prior r
 egistration required.\nYou must accompany your family or guest(s) at all 
 times during the program.\nAll children must be over the age of 5 and ful
 ly potty-trained.\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nSaturday\, April 24\, 2026\n5:00 
 pm - 9:45 pm\nStudent Recreation Center - Pool \n\nEmail us at srcaquatic
 s@montclair.edu with any questions.  We look forward to seeing you at the
  pool!\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\, Parent & Family Programs \n\nAdd
 itional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/eng
 age/event/12297467
