CATEGORIES:Social
DESCRIPTION:Get creative and design something meaningful at our Gift Bag M
 aking event! This hands-on experience is the perfect opportunity to craft
  a personalized gift bag for someone special—whether it’s for a friend\, 
 loved one\, or a mother figure in your life.\nPlease note: this is a BYOB
  (Bring Your Own Bag/items) event. Participants are expected to bring the
 ir own gift bags and any items they’d like to include—such as self-care p
