SUMMARY:Saturday with Sondheim! NEW
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nJoin us for a dynamic one-day workshop celebrating the genius 
 of Stephen Sondheim. Designed for musical theater enthusiasts of all 
 levels\, this engaging session dives into the music\, lyrics\, and 
 storytelling that define Sondheim’s legendary work. Through guided 
 discussion\, musical exploration\, and interactive group activities\, 
 participants will gain a deeper appreciation for the artistry and 
 innovation that shaped modern musical theater. Whether you're a lifelong 
 fan or just discovering his brilliance\, this workshop offers an inspiring 
 look into Sondheim’s life\, legacy\, and unforgettable contributions to 
 the stage. Come celebrate the master of modern musical theater with us!
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Classroom\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Music
UID:LibCal-10306-16014951
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/16014951
END:VEVENT
