SUMMARY:Learn how to play the Pokémon Trading Card Game (ages 6 )
DESCRIPTION:This program is aimed for beginners or folks that have never 
 played the Pokémon Trading Card Game before. We will be using Pokémon TCG 
 Battle Academy sets that have everything you need to get started. They 
 contain premade decks and tutorial guides so that you can learn the basics 
 of Pokémon battle at your own pace. You just need to read and do a little 
 bit of math!\n\nBring a friend or battle your grown-up!\n\nRegistration 
 required.
