SUMMARY:Everwalk Liberty State Park Loop Walk (joint walk with Freewalkers
 )
DESCRIPTION:EverWalk NJ\nThis is a 7-mile walk through Liberty State Park 
 with great view of the New York skyline\, the Statue of Liberty\, and bird
 s in tidal flats.\n\n**You can only register for this event on Eventbrite 
 at:**\nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/e/1986664404714?aff=oddtdtcreator\n\nThi
 s is one of the monthly Everwalk walks occurring across the country and ar
 ound the world . More information can be found at www.EverWalk.com and on 
 the EverWalk Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/groups/EverWalkNation
 /.\n\nMeet at The Central Railroad of NJ building across from the Empty Sk
 y Memorial. Parking directions are available at the Eventbrite link.
