SUMMARY:HabibiFest
DESCRIPTION:Montclair GameNights and Social Networking Meetup Group\nJoin 
 me for a group visit to HabibiFest NJ\, a celebration of Arab culture\, co
 mmunity\, and food!\n\nThis will be a relaxed meetup where we walk around 
 the festival together\, try different foods\, check out the souq (market)\
 , watch performances\, and enjoy the tea tent and cultural activities.\n\n
 The festival includes:\n• Arab food vendors\n• Souq / artisan market\n
 • Cultural performances\n• Henna art\n• Kids activities\n• Tea ten
 t and social space\n\nThe event is free and open to everyone\, so feel fre
 e to bring friends as well.\n\nMeeting Plan:\nWe’ll meet at 12:30 PM nea
 r the main entrance of The Woodland in Maplewood\, NJ. I’ll post a comme
 nt in the Meetup event on the day with the exact meeting spot.\n\nAbout Ha
 bibiFest:\nHabibiFest NJ is an annual festival celebrating Arab cultures w
 ith music\, food\, art\, and community.\n\nLooking forward to meeting ever
 yone and enjoying the festival together
