DESCRIPTION:Join us for a gorgeous hike through Hacklebarney state park. T
 he trail features the Black River as a centerpiece and is quite stunning 
 in the spring season.\n \nHow do I sign-up?\n\nRegister in the Student Re
 creation Center main office or over the phone (973-655-3340).\nCost for S
 tudents $10 | Faculty/Staff/Community $20\n\n \nWhere and when?\n\nSunday
 \, April 26th\, 2026\n10am-4pm \nBus leaves from Student Recreation Cente
 r\n\n \nWhat to bring: Water\, Lunch\, and Boots or Sneakers\n \nPotentia
 l Hazards: Unpredictable weather changes\, sunburn/heat exhaustion\, limi
 ted vision\, dehydration\, allergic reactions/poisonous plants\, insect b
 ites\, and injury by running\, including sprains\, lacerations\, abrasion
 s and fractures.\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Informatio
 n can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12267446
