DESCRIPTION:Miles Without Borders is a high-energy\, Olympic-style field d
 ay bringing together fun\, fitness\, and philanthropy! In collaboration w
 ith MSU Run for Fun\, Friends of Doctors Without Borders (FOMSF) invites 
 students to compete in exciting team-based challenges\, races\, and mini-
 games designed for all skill levels.\nThis event isn’t just about winning
 —it’s about making a difference. As part of our initiative\, we are hosti
 ng a food drive to support local communities in need. Participants and at
 tendees are encouraged to bring non-perishable food items to contribute t
 o the cause.\nCome out to run\, play\, and give back while supporting glo
 bal medical humanitarian efforts. Whether you're competing or cheering fr
 om the sidelines\, your participation helps make an impact both locally a
 nd worldwide.\nLet’s move with purpose and turn friendly competition into
  meaningful change!\n\nHosted by: Friends of Doctors Without Borders\, MS
 U Run For Fun\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://montclai
 r.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12388512
