SUMMARY:Basic Italian 1B - Online
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nIt's time to brush up on your Italian!  Basic Italian 1B is 
 for students who have taken Basic Italian I or Italian for Travelers and 
 would like to communicate more effectively in handling transactions\, 
 making reservations\, ordering in a restaurant\, asking directions…They 
 will learn how to express themselves in talking about the present and the 
 past.  If you speak another Romance language or need a quick review\, this 
 is a good beginning for your study of Italian. \n\n\nPrerequisite: Basic 
 Italian 1\, Italian for Travelers or equivalent.\n
LOCATION:Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Language
