DESCRIPTION:The North Essex Chamber of Commerce invites you to our Spring 
 Fever at Fogo Networking Event Join the North Essex Chamber of Commerce at
  Fogo do Chao in Willowbrook Mall for an exciting evening with networking\
 , refreshments\, and good times! Unwind and celebrate spring with drinks\,
  delicious food while mingling with other business professionals. NECC mem
 bers: $30\; Bring a guest for only an additional $20 Nonmembers: $45. Brin
 g a guest for only an additional $30 Discounts given upon purchase of mult
 iple tickets. Price includes passed appetizers\, and 1 drink ticket for a 
 beverage of your choice. About Fogo de Chao Fogo de Chão\, (Portuguese fo
 r 'Ground Fire') is a Brazilian rodízio-style steakhouse (churrascarias) 
 founded in 1979. The restaurant chain specializes in Southern Brazilian cu
 isine\, primarily serving churrasco barbecued meats and traditional side d
 ishes. Sponsorships Available Increase brand awareness and visibility for 
 your business by becoming a sponsor. Azalea (Event) Sponsor
