DESCRIPTION:Our annual in-person plant sale is a fabulous community event every spring. Find the highest quality annuals\, perennials\, herbs\, vegetables\, hanging baskets and special items all chosen by our Van Vleck Horticulturalist. \nMembers will enjoy first access to our Spring Plant Sale items on Members’ Evening and a 10% discount on all purchases during the sale.  Not a member? Join or renew HERE. \nInterested in finding Native Plants at our sale? Check out this informative brochure about Native Plants prepared by our partners at Bee City and Northeast Earth Coalition. \nNative Plant Benefits brochure
