SUMMARY:Volunteers Needed for Fairy Trail Day
DESCRIPTION:South Mountain Conservancy Activities Meetup Group\n**[SIGN UP
  GENIUS LINK HERE!](https://www.signupgenius.com/go/10C0849ABAB2CA7F4C61-6
 3036835-2026#/)**\n\nThe **South Mountain Conservancy** is seeking enthusi
 astic volunteers (ages **16+**) to help make our **family-friendly\, fairy
 -filled celebration** a magical success!\n\n🧚 This is a wonderful oppor
 tunity for members of our SMC community to come together and support a bel
 oved event — plus\, it’s a fun way to earn **service hours** while hel
 ping the **South Mountain Conservancy & Fairy Trail**!\n\n**Volunteer Role
 s Available (more on the Sign up Genius!):**\n🏡 Fairy House Making Stat
 ion\n🧾 Merch & Membership Table\n🚦 Traffic Directing (21+)\n🌞 Eve
 nt Greeters\n\nPlease contact Penni Malakates (opdirector@somocon.org) wit
 h any questions!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/somocon/events/313529831/
