X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_nj_code_coffee
X-SOURCE:Meetup: NJ Code & Coffee
UID:event_314235028@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260412T031144Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260502T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260502T170000
SUMMARY:NJ Code & Coffee - May meetup
DESCRIPTION:NJ Code & Coffee\nCalling all New Jersey techies to the **NJ C
 ode and Coffee** tech community meetup at the EqualSpace ES550 Tech & Inno
 vation campus!\n\nCode and Coffee is an inclusive\, informal networking/co
 -working session for those in tech (and the tech-curious).\nThat includes 
 operators\, founders\, and investors. Developers\, data engineers\, UX/UI 
 designers\, data scientists\, product managers\, software engineers\, solu
 tion architects... **all are welcome!**\n\nPeople of all skill and experie
 nce levels can attend\, we love it that way. Many people (optionally) brin
 g projects to work on\, and many other people (optionally) socialize the e
 ntire time. It's entirely up to you!\n\nCome grab a cup of coffee and meet
  new people\, share stories\, find collaborators\, talk about everything t
 ech\, talk about everything NOT tech\, take a break from job applications\
 , get away from the computer screen\, make connections\, make conversation
 \, **make friends!**\n\n**Agenda:**\n**2pm:** Doors open\, networking star
 ts\n**2:30pm:** Intro circle\n**3pm:** networking continues\n**5pm:** even
 t ends\n\n**The Intro Circle**\n**Near the beginning of the event (about 2
 :30 pm)\, we will do a standup in a circle:**\nWe first talk about organiz
 er announcements\, updates\, and logistics. Then we go around the circle w
 here each person says:\n\n*your name and job title/ role in tech/ tech sta
 ck\,\n- What you can help others with\,\n*What you would like help with\,\
 n- Job opportunities you're hiring for OR announce that you are looking fo
 r one. If none\, that's cool.\n\nAfter the introduction circle\, everythin
 g is self-organized.\n\n**Community Discord - come hang out before and aft
 er!:**\n[www.codeandcoffee.chat](www.codeandcoffee.chat)\n\n**The Venue**\
 nEqual Space is a premium share-space created with multicultural business 
 owners in mind\, =SPACE equips founders with resources\, programming and a
  powerful network.\n\nHeadquartered in the City of Newark\, their share-sp
 ace provides resources for startups\, coaching for tech companies\, and a 
 wealth of intellectuals to collaborate and build with. The next wave in en
 terprises is being born within their walls. Become a part of the story: [E
 qualSpace.co/](https://equalspace.co/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/nj-code-coffee/events/314235028/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260411T203155Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260411T203155Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
