UID:10006670-1777978800-1777982400@montclairfoundation.org
SUMMARY:Mindfulness in the Garden - Late Spring Series
DESCRIPTION:Mindfulness in the Garden (Weekday Series) \nInstructor: Jodi Brooks \nTuesdays\, 11:00 AM – 12:00 PM \nLate Spring Session: May 5\, 12\, 19 & 26 \nDiscover how a mindfulness practice can help us awaken and  live in harmony with oneself and with the natural world. This class will include: simple instructions for getting started with a formal mindfulness practice\, very gentle stretching & breathwork\, and an outdoor contemplative garden walk. This is a practice of slowing down\, cultivating quiet and paying attention to our senses. All levels are welcome. No experience needed. Winter session will be held indoors\, with a short walk outdoors (weather permitting). \nFee:  Each 4-class Series: $80 Members / $100 General Public \nSeries registration only. Pre Registration is required – there are no drop-ins for this class. \n \nEarly Summer Session: June 2\, 9\, 16 & 23 \n  \nWeekend Mindfulness class schedule: \nSaturdays\, 9:30 AM – 10:30 AM \nApril 18th \nMay 9th \nJune 13th \n 
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/mindfulness-in-the-garden-late-spring-series-2/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes,Adults
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2026/02/20250909_110627-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
