SUMMARY:The Secret Tea Room at Van Vleck
DESCRIPTION:Seating times: \nMay 9 \n11:30 AM – 1:00 PM\n12:00 PM – 1:30 PM\n1:00 PM – 2:30 PM  SOLD OUT\n2:30 PM – 4:00 PM\nJoin us for an enchanting Afternoon Tea in the House Living Room at Van Vleck House & Gardens! \nUpon arrival\, you will be offered a menu of fine teas and infusions. Your choice of tea will be brewed to perfection. Once everyone is settled in\, the tiers will arrive with freshly baked scones\, jam\, homemade clotted cream\, scrumptious sandwiches\, and\, for this Afternoon Tea\, three scrumptious desserts. We hope you will join us! \nThis event is for adults and children ages 13+. Seatings are 90 minutes\, and registration is required. \nDietary Restrictions\nA gluten-free option is available with prior notice. We are not able to accommodate a dairy-free or vegan diet. All requests must be communicated to us 48 hours before the event. You may note this request on the checkout page. \nMember Price: $55\nNon-Member Price: $65\nA 10% gratuity for your server is included in tea pricing.
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/the-secret-tea-room-at-van-vleck-7/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Events,Adults
