DESCRIPTION:<span>Green Team/Creation Justice Ministry monthly meetings: 2
 nd Sunday of the month\, after worship\, in the FCC library. </span><span
 > </span><span><span><span>Our congregation is committed to the idea that
  creation care is central to each aspect of our church: our theology and w
 orship\, institutional life and practices\, and our partnership and work i
 n the wider community. </span></span></span><span>Learn about FCC’s cli
 mate justice initiatives\, be part of planning our events\, and live your 
 faith by taking action for the planet. </span><br><span>Check out our Gre
 en Team Ministry page here: </span><a href="https://fccmontclair.org/gree
 n-team-ministry/" target="_blank">https://fccmontclair.org/green-team-mini
 stry/</a><span> <br></span><span>and read our Creation Justice Covenant he
 re: <a href="https://www.fccmontclair.org/creation-justice-church/" targe
 t="_blank">https://www.fccmontclair.org/creation-justice-church/</a></span
 ><br><span>Contact Green Team at <a href="mailto:greenteam@fccmtc.com" ta
 rget="_blank">greenteam@fccmtc.com</a>.</span>
