SUMMARY:Second Sunday Concert: New Jersey Symphony Brass Quintet on Mother's Day
DESCRIPTION:May 10 – Annual Mother’s Day brass quintet concert on the Bingham formal lawn at Van Vleck Gardens. \nPlease bring a blanket or lawn chair. \nNo pets\, food or alcoholic beverages are permitted. \nThe event is weather-dependent so please check our website if the forecast is uncertain. \nThe registration link will be sent to Series Patrons\, Members and then posted here for the general public in April.
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/second-sunday-concert-nj-symphony-on-mothers-day/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Events,Adults,Family
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2025/10/USATSI_20667251-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
