DESCRIPTION:Whether in your own home or someone else’s\, with one person
  or many\, having an elaborate meal or ordering take-out\, there is not on
 e way to celebrate Shabbat. “Shabbat Your Way” is an opportunity to cu
 ltivate a Shabbat mindset in a way that feels right for you. Shomrei will 
 provide resources and ideas to help you add something new or special to yo
 ur Shabbat practice or gathering.  \n  \n  \n**Season Schedule**  \nhttps:
 //shomrei.org/calendar/shabbat-your-way-calendar\n\n
