SUMMARY:Meeting at the Verona inn!
DESCRIPTION:Board Game Night At Verona Inn\nWe will be doing our first mon
 thly meeting starting on **February 25th at the Verona Inn!** We will be m
 eeting up to organize games starting at 7:30\, with food and drinks availa
 ble courtesy of our host! You can play any game provided by hosts or bring
  your own! If you do not have a friend group to play games\, hosts will or
 ganize you into pods with other people who need players. There are **no du
 es**. Future meetings will be held on the **last Wednesday of each month.*
 *\n\nMore information and ground rules:\n\n* **The doors open at 6:30 but 
 games do not start until 7:30.** I *highly recommend* coming in during thi
 s period to eat your food and drink ahead of time!\n*\n* **Please return t
 he graciousness provided by our hosts and order at least one item! All ven
 ue specific rules apply to our club.** Future meetings depend on treating 
 our hosts with respect.\n* **All games must be returned to their owners wh
 en they announce that they are leaving.** If you are in a game in progress
  when the meeting ends but it is not borrowed you may continue playing!\n*
  **Please place food and drink on a separate table or surface from your ga
 mes** to help avoid stains and other damage.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/board-game-night-at-verona-inn/events
 /wrdqwtyjchbhc/
