 -bulletin/">this week's online bulletin</a> here.</span> <br></p><p><span
 ><b><u>FCC Parking Lot:</u> The Plymouth St. driveway is permanently close
 d. Enter from The Crescent. Please drive slowly\, our new driveway is next
  to the playground. </b></span></p><u></u><u></u><u></u>
