DESCRIPTION:<p>This is our LBGTQ+ community within FCC which gathers for s
 ocial events and spiritual conversations. We meet weekly on<span> Sundays
  during coffee hour\, in Room 5 (Parents Room!)</span> We meet to introduc
 e ourselves\, hang out\, and chat about life\, spirituality\, and whatever
  else comes up! If you are interested in joining this group\, please<span>
  contact Jordan at </span><a href="mailto:fullspectrum@fccmtc.com" target=
 "_blank"><u><span>fullspectrum@fccmtc.com</span></u></a><span>.</span></p>
