SUMMARY:Green Team Ministry meeting (2nd Sundays) 12-1pm in FCC Library
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260614T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260614T130000
DTSTAMP:20260412T031140Z
UID:bul8ku40hd689i3ku2pmme3kje@google.com__20260614
SEQUENCE:2
CREATED:20250203T162635Z
DESCRIPTION:<span>Green Team/Creation Justice Ministry monthly meetings: 2
 nd Sunday of the month\, after worship\, in the FCC library. </span><span
 > </span><span><span><span>Our congregation is committed to the idea that
  creation care is central to each aspect of our church: our theology and w
 orship\, institutional life and practices\, and our partnership and work i
 n the wider community. </span></span></span><span>Learn about FCC’s cli
 mate justice initiatives\, be part of planning our events\, and live your 
