DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260626T091500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260626T101500
SUMMARY:Eagle Rock Reservation
DESCRIPTION:Let's Walk!!\nJOIN US FOR A WALK. WE WALK AT A MODERATE PACE O
 N UNPAVED PATHS.\n\nWe will hike for about an hour - 3.5 miles. We will be
  walking on trails in the woods\, so appropriate footwear\, long pants & s
 ocks\, and bug spray.\n\nWill will meet at:\n[https://goo.gl/maps/7rRRTiXC
 ntdE1neD7](https://goo.gl/maps/7rRRTiXCntdE1neD7) Eagle Rock Trail Parking
  Lot by Kiosk#1\n\nIf you enter from Eagle Rock Way\, go pass the Highlawn
  and stay left. There will be a parking lot at the end of the curve to you
 r right.\n\nEagle Rock Reservation is 408 acres of hills\, streams\, and v
 alleys located on the borders of West Orange\, Verona\, and Montclair\, Ne
 w Jersey. Though located in the middle of the most densely populated count
 y in the most densely populated state in the country\, the Reservation is 
 mostly undeveloped and boasts an extensive trail system within its borders
 .\n\n**Please make sure to RSVP and arrive 5 minutes prior to start time.*
 *\n\nFOLLOW US ON INSTAGRAM - letswalkmeetup\n\nDisclaimer: If you join us
  for a hike\, please understand that you are responsible for your own prep
 aredness and well-being and will hold no one else liable in case of injury
  or mishap. Event will be canceled in the event of extreme weather.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lets-walkprogram/events/sqdsftyjcjbjc
 /
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20230629T233908Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20230629T233908Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
